{"tid":922313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係碼頭食左個後生處女","createTime":"2018-11-30T09:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T10:07:55.000Z","uid":89555,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"40343b2d3426c69989c3c8ab83bc756017c72ec5","tid":922313,"uid":89555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"係以前間濕尻大型碼頭公司返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每年暑假都有班撚樣入黎做實習<br />\n間唔中都會有囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能平時啲囡返學對撚住毛都未生齊既同學仔<br />\n成熟既男人特別容易吸引後生囡 所以啲囡其實好易yo<br />\n有一年yo左個矮妹 佢細細粒 外表成日楚楚可憐咁<br />\n但實質內裡火爆 霸道 就想試下做果時有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知原來係處女黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後佢仲入左黎公司做parttime<br />\n佢又好抵得諗 早我一個鐘收工都肯搵地方等埋我收工<br />\n我擔任接送佢返工返學既職責<br />\n不過條囡脾氣太臭 加上我正印同佢同一部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又咁撚岩負責教佢<br />\n我唔想搞大件事 就好快同佢散左<br />\n當初以為佢會因為咁就唔撚做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲好大方咁繼續同我有聯絡 有講有笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又會介紹其他囡比我加ig<br />\n有時我去搵正印吹水 佢又會扮撚晒野咁行埋黎搵人吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到最後佢係帶埋佢現任既男朋友一齊入撚晒公司到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但間唔中都繼續有同我whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係公司好多人都知條囡易食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望住佢條仔頭頂頂帽真係好撚好笑"},{"pid":"3c8c12ffac6b78364b9790017adb9f0754d1c3bd","tid":922313,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"可唔可以教我點溝女"},{"pid":"521c63bb463198cc8de7400c23f5ef6c92162ea1","tid":922313,"uid":82482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"1.5/10<br />\n嗰分半係俾冇是咁的"},{"pid":"d9339981ac3fc8aafa08bec9a3764f62241e1029","tid":922313,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/04/27/204340_e2f2fa939acc0520439837c3c24d3375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F04%2F27%2F204340_e2f2fa939acc0520439837c3c24d3375.jpg&h=6c7f7157&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f04eb26671d5d890f23aeb811a4014e3496378c","tid":922313,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3005ac5dc844ac53b14414d27220904eaca7cddd","tid":922313,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:03:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8260cfa1a43e11f148918e502c6c0a5559d550b3","tid":922313,"uid":67201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的"}]}